This paper deals with the optimization of UAV trajectories for cellular communication, which involves topics such as networked control systems, information theory, and machine learning. Therefore, the most likely sub-category is cs.NI (Networking and Internet Architecture). The paper also involves optimization of the UAV's flight path, which falls under the sub-category cs.RO (Robotics). The paper also discusses outage duration, which is a topic in information theory and communication systems, falling under the sub-category cs.IT (Information Theory). The paper also involves constraints and optimization, which are topics in control systems and optimization, falling under the sub-categories cs.SY (Systems and Control) and cs.LG (Machine Learning).
